  "texts": [
    "Thus, the integration of verifier models complemented and compensated for the limitations of the DA, leading to more efficient use of the feedback loop in the design process.",
    "4) This study demonstrated that GPT-3.5-Turbo with the TVDL strategy enabled the smaller model to surpass the performance of its larger counterpart GPT-4-Turbo.",
    "This was achieved at a two and a half times lower cost, highlighting the effectiveness of using post-training enhancements such as test-time strategies and verifier models.",
    "In summary, this study demonstrates the of LLMs in AAC design and provides a novel path for future AI applications in materials science.",
    "Our findings highlight how LLMs can advance sustainable materials design, contributing to environmental goals and enriching the role of AI in materials engineering."
